00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:11,786
Jedan jedini put...

241
00:15:11,950 --> 00:15:15,909
Nije jedan put, svaki put !
Vec 15 godina !

242
00:15:16,070 --> 00:15:18,789
Inace, ne bih bila u ovom stanju.

243
00:15:18,950 --> 00:15:22,067
Rekla bih :
"Pa nije vazno Vini."

244
00:15:22,230 --> 00:15:23,709
Uvek je tako !

245
00:15:23,870 --> 00:15:26,145
Nikad necu nista zabavno doziveti.

246
00:15:26,830 --> 00:15:28,104
Volim zabavu !

247
00:15:32,110 --> 00:15:34,066
Mogu li stvarno da pricam sa tobom ?

248
00:15:34,230 --> 00:15:36,141
Naravno, Dot.

249
00:15:39,430 --> 00:15:41,022
Violet, kako si ?

250
00:15:42,310 --> 00:15:44,460
Poznajes Dot.
Dot, Violet...

251
00:15:46,510 --> 00:15:47,147
Je'l ide ?

252
00:15:47,310 --> 00:15:50,427
Stizem... Cekaj da kazem.
Samo da ti kazem...

253
00:15:50,590 --> 00:15:55,220
da u subotu uvece ti i ja idemo na
"gins-gins", secas se ?

254
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:58,908
Ides da igras ?
Ne otkazuj.

255
00:15:59,070 --> 00:16:00,219
Vidimo se !

256
00:16:00,390 --> 00:16:01,425
Slusaj...

257
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,862
Ne otkazuj, ha ?

258
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:05,179
Ne mi !

259
00:16:05,350 --> 00:16:07,739
Ni Vini ne otkazuje.

260
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:09,662
Ne seri !

261
00:16:12,310 --> 00:16:13,584
Budi dobar !

262
00:16:15,150 --> 00:16:16,469
Kako si, seksi ?

263
00:16:16,630 --> 00:16:19,190
A ti ?
Drago mi je da te vidim srce moje.

264
00:16:21,070 --> 00:16:25,143
Toi et moi, on fait guinche-guinche,
Ok? Samedi soir.

265
00:16:25,430 --> 00:16:26,704
U subotu uvece ?

266
00:16:28,710 --> 00:16:31,270
Ne ove subote, sledece.

267
00:16:31,430 --> 00:16:33,660
Ne zezas, Ogi !

268
00:16:33,830 --> 00:16:36,788
- Sta to radis ?
- Ti, sta mi to radis ?

269
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:39,585
Prestani, mora da cisti.

270
00:16:41,350 --> 00:16:44,387
Obecao si !
Sta sad izigravas ?

271
00:16:44,550 --> 00:16:49,066
Rekli smo sesnaestog, ok ?
Organizovala sam to vece.

272
00:16:49,670 --> 00:16:52,707
Je'l to zarazno ?
Sta ti je ?

273
00:16:52,870 --> 00:16:55,179
Dot nije dobra a ni ti.

274
00:16:55,350 --> 00:16:57,739
- Sta to imas u usima ?
- Moju muziku.

275
00:16:59,710 --> 00:17:02,065
Slusaj, duso. U subotu uvece...

276
00:17:05,830 --> 00:17:08,708
U subotu uvece obecao sam Tomiju...

277
00:17:08,910 --> 00:17:12,698
Da cu da ispraznim stan njegovog brata s njim.
Znas, njegovog brata...

278
00:17:13,590 --> 00:17:15,387
Njegov brat Cak.

279
00:17:15,750 --> 00:17:17,149
Bili smo...

280
00:17:18,070 --> 00:17:20,504
u marincima zajedno.
Umro je.

281
00:17:21,870 --> 00:17:23,986
- Razumes ?
- O cemu pricas ?

282
00:17:24,190 --> 00:17:27,148
Cak ?
Jebi ga, ko je taj Cak ?

283
00:17:28,030 --> 00:17:30,703
Ne. "Jebi ga, ko je taj Cak ?"
Umro je.

284
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:34,188
Bio je u marincima sa mnom.
Umro je.

285
00:17:35,270 --> 00:17:38,979
Ti me varas, srce ?

286
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:42,385
Da te varam ?
Prelepa si da bih te varao !

287
00:17:42,550 --> 00:17:43,699
S kim ?

288
00:17:47,870 --> 00:17:49,667
Znam !

289
00:17:49,830 --> 00:17:52,867
Mala konobarica sa velikim dupetom,
je'l tako ?

290
00:17:53,030 --> 00:17:55,339
Precenjujes me !

291
00:17:55,510 --> 00:17:58,422
Nikad te ne bih varao.
Sta ti je ?

292
00:17:58,790 --> 00:18:00,940
Volim te. Ajde prekini.

293
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:25,459
Lagao si me, Agosto.

294
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:29,226
A ljudi koji lazu,

295
00:18:29,390 --> 00:18:32,427
ne zasluzuju da ih neko voli.

296
00:18:33,950 --> 00:18:36,669
Ako se zajebavas sa Violetom,

297
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:40,186
Violeta se brani.

298
00:18:49,030 --> 00:18:53,421
Zaklacu te Ogi.

299
00:18:54,790 --> 00:18:56,746
Kao tigar.

300
00:18:56,910 --> 00:18:59,060
Kao jebani tigar !

301
00:18:59,510 --> 00:19:01,341
Mojim zubima.

302
00:19:04,710 --> 00:19:08,589
Ostri su kao zileti.

303
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:15,468
Ne zezaj se sa mnom !

304
00:19:16,390 --> 00:19:19,268
Da, devojke iz Brooklyn-a znaju da se biju.

305
00:19:19,430 --> 00:19:21,421
Cupamo se za kosu,

306
00:19:21,590 --> 00:19:25,549
Bijemo se kao muskarci.
Pesnicama !

307
00:19:25,710 --> 00:19:28,588
Ako je druga jaca, koristimo

308
00:19:28,750 --> 00:19:30,786
flasu ili bilo sta.

309
00:19:30,950 --> 00:19:32,906
Imam li decka ? Da.

310
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:34,867
Ali je saban.

311
00:19:35,030 --> 00:19:39,023
Nije kao ja. Ne voli da gleda stvari,
da bude kul.

312
00:19:39,190 --> 00:19:41,579
Samo hoce da pusi travicu

313
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:44,503
i da pije pivo ceo dan.

314
00:19:45,070 --> 00:19:49,985
Samo to radi... Sigurno pusi
pola kile trave dnevno.

315
00:19:50,150 --> 00:19:52,459
Promenicu ja to.

316
00:19:52,630 --> 00:19:55,508
Suvise ima Brooklyn-a u krvi.

317
00:20:09,190 --> 00:20:10,464
Paket Lucky-ja ?

318
00:20:10,630 --> 00:20:11,904
Znas sta ?

319
00:20:12,230 --> 00:20:13,629
Ne.

320
00:20:13,830 --> 00:20:16,344
Ostala mi je jedna cigareta,

321
00:20:16,510 --> 00:20:19,343
i odlucio sam da dodjem...
Prekidam sa pusenjem,

322
00:20:19,510 --> 00:20:21,705
ali sam hteo da poslednju popusim s tobom.

323
00:20:21,870 --> 00:20:26,022
Rekao sam sebi: "Poslednju ces de popusis
sa Ogijem."

324
00:20:26,430 --> 00:20:27,829
Dirnut sam.

325
00:20:27,990 --> 00:20:31,665
Hoces da me slikas sa Ogijem
i sa poslednjom pljugom ?

326
00:20:31,830 --> 00:20:33,661
Samo pritisni ovde.

327
00:20:34,430 --> 00:20:36,022
Poslednja.

328
00:20:36,950 --> 00:20:38,702
Gde da stanem ?

329
00:20:38,870 --> 00:20:41,464
Ne znam.
Hoces ovde ?

330
00:20:53,190 --> 00:20:54,828
Poslednja pljuga.
Sa Ogijem.

331
00:20:54,990 --> 00:20:57,379
Dirnut sam da poslednja bude sa mnom.

332
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:59,905
12 godina kupujem ovde moj Lucky.

333
00:21:00,070 --> 00:21:02,630
Stani Dzimi.
Prst ti je ispred.

334
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:16,585
Poslednja.

335
00:21:16,750 --> 00:21:19,264
Secam se moje prve pljuge.

336
00:21:20,110 --> 00:21:23,068
Moji drugari su maznuli cigarete

337
00:21:23,230 --> 00:21:26,461
u "Bueler's Pharmacy",
u jednom predgradju u Ohaju,

338
00:21:26,630 --> 00:21:27,904
tamo sam odrastao.

339
00:21:28,070 --> 00:21:30,789
Vratili smo se kuci uz prugu.

340
00:21:30,950 --> 00:21:34,499
Otvorili smo paket.
Bile su to New Port cigarete.

341
00:21:34,670 --> 00:21:36,308
Prvo smo ih onjusili.

342
00:21:36,470 --> 00:21:38,745
Mentolne mirisu kao bombone.

343
00:21:38,910 --> 00:21:42,459
Upalili smo, uvukli dim i
poceli da kasljemo.

344
00:21:42,630 --> 00:21:45,224
Par minuta posle nam je bilo muka.

345
00:21:45,390 --> 00:21:47,506
Ali smo se osecali kul.

346
00:21:47,670 --> 00:21:50,309
Prave face... Balavci od 10 godina !

347
00:21:50,470 --> 00:21:53,860
Seks i cigarete, moram da priznam...

348
00:21:54,190 --> 00:21:57,944
da ce mi to faliti...

349
00:21:58,710 --> 00:22:02,544
Prekidas i sa seksom ? Jer vise neces
moci da pusis posle ?

350
00:22:02,710 --> 00:22:04,223
Moje devojke sve puse...

351
00:22:04,390 --> 00:22:07,302
ako prekinem, mozda vise
necu voditi ljubav !

352
00:22:07,470 --> 00:22:10,189
Cigareta posle seksa,

353
00:22:10,350 --> 00:22:13,786
ima takav ukus ! Ona koju podelis
se svojom ljubavnicom...

354
00:22:13,950 --> 00:22:14,905
Raj !

355
00:22:15,070 --> 00:22:16,219
To ce mi faliti.

356
00:22:16,390 --> 00:22:19,109
I uz kafu.
Kafa i cigareta...

357
00:22:19,270 --> 00:22:20,988
Dorucak sampiona !

358
00:22:24,790 --> 00:22:26,382
Hoces kafu ?

359
00:22:26,550 --> 00:22:29,064
Ne prljaj se covece !

360
00:22:29,230 --> 00:22:31,027
Ma ne brini.

361
00:22:31,190 --> 00:22:32,543
Imam jedno pitanje.

362
00:22:32,710 --> 00:22:36,100
Imam intervju za posao na broju 209 i po.

363
00:22:36,270 --> 00:22:40,388
Ima li neke bolnicarka u blizini ?

364
00:22:40,550 --> 00:22:42,700
Ima bolnica na 5 ulica odavde.

365
00:22:42,870 --> 00:22:45,100
Znam. Upravo izlazim iz bolnice.

366
00:22:45,270 --> 00:22:47,420
Vrati se tamo.
Da te ponovo obaviju.

367
00:22:47,830 --> 00:22:49,900
To je upravo uradjeno.

368
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:51,305
Koji je dan danas ?

369
00:22:51,470 --> 00:22:53,700
Danas ? Sreda.

370
00:22:54,830 --> 00:22:55,819
Sta trazis ?

371
00:22:55,990 --> 00:22:57,946
Broj 209 i po.

372
00:22:58,110 --> 00:22:59,384
Ovde je 211.

373
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:01,308
209 je preko puta...

374
00:23:01,550 --> 00:23:04,223
Ne, ovo je 209.

375
00:23:04,390 --> 00:23:07,302
211. Ovo je 209... 211.

376
00:23:07,470 --> 00:23:09,267
209 i po je zaglavljen ovde.

377
00:23:09,430 --> 00:23:12,467
Nisu mi potrebni svi ti detalji.
Nemas pojma.

378
00:23:12,710 --> 00:23:15,986
Nismo mi brojevi u Brooklyn-u.
Sta hoces ?

379
00:23:16,150 --> 00:23:19,699
4,95 dolara.
Da kupim "belgian waffle" (kolac).

380
00:23:20,670 --> 00:23:22,342
Trazis 4,95 dolara !

381
00:23:22,510 --> 00:23:23,909
Remek delo !

382
00:23:24,070 --> 00:23:26,300
Predivno ! Ne prave ih vise.

383
00:23:26,470 --> 00:23:29,064
Prosla moda.
Ne prave vise takve.

384
00:23:29,230 --> 00:23:32,381
Samo jos nase mame prave takve.
Vise ih nema.

385
00:23:44,350 --> 00:23:49,060
Poruka:
Oblacimo se u zavisnosti od odredista

386
00:23:49,430 --> 00:23:50,943
U Brooklyn-u imamo sve.

387
00:23:51,110 --> 00:23:54,500
Ima malih reka...

388
00:23:54,670 --> 00:23:59,141
ljudi to ne znaju.
Ima vodopada.

389
00:24:01,070 --> 00:24:04,665
Fantasticno :
strasan kvart, gde svega ima.

390
00:24:04,830 --> 00:24:08,789
Ravnih terena, izdignutih,
na vise nivoa, sumovitih.

391
00:24:09,950 --> 00:24:11,463
Cak i mocvara.

392
00:24:11,630 --> 00:24:15,066
Ako poredimo sve kvartove,

393
00:24:15,230 --> 00:24:17,107
Brooklyn je najveci.

394
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:20,501
I naj-kul.

395
00:24:22,510 --> 00:24:25,263
Gledajte ovo. Ima satova.

396
00:24:25,430 --> 00:24:29,582
NE samo Swatch, nego i
Seiko, Casio, Timex, Rolex

397
00:24:29,750 --> 00:24:32,105
Za seks
Treba lateks

398
00:24:32,270 --> 00:24:34,022
Imam sve sto treba !

399
00:24:34,190 --> 00:24:35,748
Uzimam sve.

400
00:24:35,950 --> 00:24:39,147
Bez zezanja, svidja ti se moj EPP rep ?

401
00:24:39,310 --> 00:24:43,462
Imam dobre prilike za tebe,
Mister Brooklyn Cigar Company.

402
00:24:43,630 --> 00:24:44,346
Sta imas ?

403
00:24:44,510 --> 00:24:47,422
Imam ih po 20 i po 25 dolara.

404
00:24:48,590 --> 00:24:51,741
Africka cena, evropska cena.
Koju hoces ?

405
00:24:51,910 --> 00:24:54,265
Africka ? Evropska ?
Pokazi.

406
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:57,706
Baci oko, mali moj.
Objasnicu ti za minut.

407
00:24:57,870 --> 00:25:01,783
Prvo da se pobrinem za Afrikanca.
Crnci prvo, uvek.

408
00:25:01,950 --> 00:25:02,541
Roleks ?

409
00:25:02,710 --> 00:25:04,746
Prava, krokodilska koza.

410
00:25:04,910 --> 00:25:06,389
Gde si to nabavio ?

411
00:25:06,590 --> 00:25:10,981
Ne brini. Imam robu.
Nema problema.

412
00:25:11,150 --> 00:25:15,268
Prodajes mi je za 20,25,30,40,50 ?
Koliko ?

413
00:25:15,430 --> 00:25:16,783
Africka cena ?

414
00:25:16,950 --> 00:25:18,747
- Kako to ?
- 25 dolara.

415
00:25:18,910 --> 00:25:19,945
Nisam Afrikanac.

416
00:25:20,110 --> 00:25:25,059
Ima 872 702 Afro-Amerikanaca...

417
00:25:25,230 --> 00:25:28,108
412 906 Jevreja...

418
00:25:28,270 --> 00:25:32,661
462 411 juzno-amerikanaca u Brooklyn-u.

419
00:25:32,990 --> 00:25:36,346
Imenuj mi jednoj crnju koji visi u kvartu.
Sta ti trazis ovde ?

420
00:25:36,510 --> 00:25:39,422
Zovem se Tomi Faneli.
To je moje ime.

421
00:25:39,590 --> 00:25:41,342
Tomi Faneli ? Va bene?

422
00:25:41,510 --> 00:25:44,866
Jesi li iz Brooklyn-a ili ?
Vidi ti njega !

423
00:25:45,030 --> 00:25:45,985
Milost !

424
00:25:46,150 --> 00:25:49,699
Zasto visis ovde ?
Crown Heights. Howard Beach !

425
00:25:49,870 --> 00:25:51,144
U Brooklyn-u smo, drugar.

426
00:25:51,310 --> 00:25:54,029
A Bed-Stuy, to je ono najbolje.
Odatle sam ja.

427
00:25:54,190 --> 00:25:57,262
- To je moj kvart.
- Odakle ti to ime ?

428
00:25:57,430 --> 00:25:58,909
Poreklom sam iz Italije.

429
00:25:59,070 --> 00:26:01,345
Otac mi je italijan, keva crnkinja.

430
00:26:02,870 --> 00:26:06,499
Melez !
Ma daj, crn si koliko i ja !

431
00:26:07,110 --> 00:26:09,226
Otkud ti znas sta sam ja ?

432
00:26:09,630 --> 00:26:11,541
- Slusaj, crni covece...
- Ti pretpostavljas.

433
00:26:11,710 --> 00:26:14,304
Slusajn crni covece, brate...

434
00:26:14,470 --> 00:26:17,428
brate Faneli, slusaj.

435
00:26:17,590 --> 00:26:20,343
Smiri se. Izadji iz tog tripa.

436
00:26:25,150 --> 00:26:28,267
Izvinite, mister.
Timex, Rolex, Casio, Seiko.

437
00:26:28,430 --> 00:26:31,263
Imam sve sto vam treba !

438
00:26:31,430 --> 00:26:34,502
Ajde, pokusavam da prodam ove satove.

439
00:26:34,670 --> 00:26:37,264
Ali u stvari sam reper.

440
00:26:37,430 --> 00:26:40,422
Repujem. Volite rep ?
Ti, ne.

441
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:42,228
A ni ti sigurno!

442
00:26:42,390 --> 00:26:45,700
Hocu da kupim uredjaje.
Ocete li mi kupiti jednu ?

443
00:26:47,630 --> 00:26:48,619
Sta ?

444
00:27:01,190 --> 00:27:03,784
Sta im je svima ?
Vi ste Portorikanac ?

445
00:27:03,950 --> 00:27:05,019
Jesi li crnac ?

446
00:27:05,190 --> 00:27:07,579
Billy Ray Cyrus ! (country pevac)
Sta je sa ovim kvartom ?

447
00:27:08,510 --> 00:27:10,466
Svi biste da budete belci !

448
00:27:10,630 --> 00:27:14,669
Da svirate akusticne instrumente...
kantri muziku !

449
00:27:14,910 --> 00:27:16,502
Odakle si ?

450
00:27:18,910 --> 00:27:22,539
Bio sam iz Afrike.
Kidnapovali su nas iz Afrike.

451
00:27:22,710 --> 00:27:24,587
Crni covek, Faneli.

452
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:27,184
Ja sam te doveo iz Afrike ?
A je'l mogu da te vratim ?

453
00:27:32,590 --> 00:27:35,900
Nisam mogao da budem nesrecniji

454
00:27:36,150 --> 00:27:39,062
svih 8 godina koliko sam odrastao
u Brooklyn-u.

455
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:41,222
Ali realno,

456
00:27:41,910 --> 00:27:46,188
Na Long Island-u, mi je bilo jos gore.

457
00:27:46,350 --> 00:27:50,309
U mom detinjstu je bilo jos nekih trauma

458
00:27:50,470 --> 00:27:52,540
Osim odlaska Dodgers-a iz Brooklyn-a

459
00:27:52,710 --> 00:27:55,270
zbog kog, ako bolje razmislimo, opravdava

460
00:27:55,430 --> 00:27:59,708
to da smo svi puni nepopravljivog cinizma.

461
00:27:59,870 --> 00:28:03,749
Nemoguce je biti navijac Mets-a.
Ni Yankees-a.

462
00:28:03,910 --> 00:28:06,344
Znaci, base-ball je ispao iz tvog zivota.

463
00:28:06,990 --> 00:28:09,220
Jer si rodjen u Brooklyn-u.

464
00:28:09,390 --> 00:28:12,427
- Kad ste bili dete, voleli ste Dodgerse ?
- Veoma.

465
00:28:13,230 --> 00:28:15,221
Iako ne volim base-ball.

466
00:28:15,390 --> 00:28:18,302
Mozda zato sto vise nema Dodgersa.

467
00:28:18,470 --> 00:28:22,224
Sad kad se pomenu Dodgersi,
svi misle na Los Angeles !

468
00:28:22,390 --> 00:28:24,699
Ne govorim o njima.

469
00:28:25,190 --> 00:28:26,225
Ali...

470
00:28:27,350 --> 00:28:29,466
Long Island, to je bilo strasno.

471
00:28:29,630 --> 00:28:34,101
Stvarno strasno. U Brooklyn-u, smo
bar mogli da se setamo.

472
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:35,942
Ja sam iz Brooklyn-a, ortak.

473
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:37,907
Znas li neku melodiju iz Brooklyn-a ?

474
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:28,949
Daj mi to.

475
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:30,304
- Sviras ?
- Malo.

476
00:29:30,470 --> 00:29:32,426
Prodaje satove, svira...

477
00:29:33,950 --> 00:29:35,508
Rekao sam vam.

478
00:29:43,110 --> 00:29:44,702
Slusajte ovo, vidite ovo,

479
00:29:44,870 --> 00:29:47,259
Kupite moje lude satove

480
00:29:47,430 --> 00:29:49,307
Tacno vreme
Strasne rime

481
00:29:49,470 --> 00:29:53,986
Izgubio si se crnjo.
Seo si na to dupe crno.

482
00:29:54,150 --> 00:29:58,621
Lako je belcu
Gleda me u pravcu

483
00:29:58,790 --> 00:30:01,543
Boli te dupe, znam...

484
00:30:03,190 --> 00:30:04,908
Ono sto najvise volim u Brooklyn-u

485
00:30:05,070 --> 00:30:08,779
to je sto ima svih nacionalnosti.

486
00:30:10,030 --> 00:30:13,261
Ono sto mi se najmanje svidja,
to je sto svi ti ljudi...

487
00:30:13,430 --> 00:30:15,819
ne mogu nikako da se sloze.

488
00:30:16,990 --> 00:30:23,828
Ima 3 268 121 kokosija gnezda u Brooklyn-u.

489
00:30:24,110 --> 00:30:26,624
Puno ljudi posnu da puse

490
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:29,429
zbog "glamour"-a, kao u filmovima.

491
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:31,979
Vidis Marlona Brando-a,

492
00:30:32,150 --> 00:30:34,903
vidis Jamesa Dean-ankako puse.

493
00:30:35,430 --> 00:30:36,226
Marlene Dietrich.

494
00:30:36,390 --> 00:30:38,381
Tako sam ja poceo.

495
00:30:38,550 --> 00:30:42,668
Kad sam bio klinja video sam "Komandos smrti".

496
00:30:42,830 --> 00:30:43,819
Je'l ti poznato ?

497
00:30:44,670 --> 00:30:46,308
Richard Conte.

498
00:30:47,430 --> 00:30:49,421
Glumi... Uostalom zaboravio sam...

499
00:30:49,830 --> 00:30:52,788
Za vreme drugog svetskog rata, oni su
vojnici u evropi.

500
00:30:52,950 --> 00:30:56,784
Richard Conte je mitraljezac.
njegov pomocnik nosi municiju,

501
00:30:56,950 --> 00:31:00,738
ili mitraljez.
Oni upravo hodaju i pricaju.

502
00:31:00,910 --> 00:31:04,664
Conte prica o zivotu.
I odjednom kaze : "Jednu pljugu !"

503
00:31:04,830 --> 00:31:08,106
Il n'a jamais de cigarettes.
Njegov drugar uzdahne

504
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:09,345
i da mu jednu.

505
00:31:09,510 --> 00:31:13,901
I videti Richarda Conte-a,
sa njegovim mitraljezom da kaze :

506
00:31:14,270 --> 00:31:15,339
"Jednu pljugu !"

507
00:31:15,590 --> 00:31:17,148
propusilo mi se.

508
00:31:17,310 --> 00:31:19,221
Ovako sam govorio sa ortacima :

509
00:31:19,390 --> 00:31:22,939
"Jednu pljugu !"
"Ne zezaj !" bi rekli oni.

510
00:31:23,110 --> 00:31:25,544
Kad smo kod filmova, nevezano,

511
00:31:25,710 --> 00:31:29,100
gledao sam televiziju pre neko vece.

512
00:31:29,350 --> 00:31:31,784
Bio je neki film.

513
00:31:31,950 --> 00:31:34,942
Zasto kad ima neka pucnjava

514
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:38,705
i kad nemaju vise municije,
oni bacaju oruzje ?

515
00:31:38,870 --> 00:31:42,067
Kao plasticni upaljac.
Bez veze !

516
00:31:42,230 --> 00:31:45,745
Oruzje je skupo.
Zar ne mogu da ga ponovo napune ?

517
00:31:45,910 --> 00:31:48,743
Uvek bacaju oruzje !

518
00:31:48,910 --> 00:31:49,979
Stvarno.

519
00:31:50,150 --> 00:31:54,746
Jos nesto mi se cini cudnim.
Nacisti u filmovima...

520
00:31:54,910 --> 00:31:58,505
Zasto uvek puse na cudan nacin, ovako ?

521
00:31:59,550 --> 00:32:02,906
"Sve cete priznati, Ogi." (nemacki akcenat)

522
00:32:03,350 --> 00:32:06,820
Je'l to pretnja mucenjem ?

523
00:32:06,990 --> 00:32:08,548
Ili rade ovo :

524
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:12,659
"Znamo ko ste i sta ste uradili." (opet akcenat)

525
00:32:12,830 --> 00:32:17,540
Bez veze je sto...
Hollywood nas je nacinio da budemo zavisni,

526
00:32:17,710 --> 00:32:21,862
a kad sad tamo idemo,
nigde ne moze da se pusi.

527
00:32:22,030 --> 00:32:25,625
Upalis pljugu u nekom restoranu posle klope :

528
00:32:25,790 --> 00:32:29,339
"Zao nam je, zakonski je zabranjeno pusenje u restoranu."

529
00:32:29,510 --> 00:32:31,740
Pa zbog njih smo i poceli !

530
00:32:33,390 --> 00:32:34,743
Jednu pljugu !

531
00:32:35,070 --> 00:32:36,549
Dao sam ti !

532
00:32:36,710 --> 00:32:39,429
Poslao sam je kuci.
Tamo ih dele na porcije.

533
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:41,148
Jednu pljugu !

534
00:32:43,110 --> 00:32:44,304
Sibicu.

535
00:32:45,270 --> 00:32:46,385
Hvala.

536
00:32:46,870 --> 00:32:48,747
Isplati se imati prijatelje.

537
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:52,467
Pusim a imam puno prijatelja
koji su od toga umrli.

538
00:32:52,630 --> 00:32:55,303
Ali dok pusim

539
00:32:55,470 --> 00:32:58,462
ne popijem flasu viskija

540
00:32:58,870 --> 00:33:03,227
za 15 minuta. Sa te tacke gledista,
pusiti je dobro za zdravlje.

541
00:33:04,310 --> 00:33:06,505
Moja prva cigareta, zaboravio sam.

542
00:33:06,670 --> 00:33:10,902
Secam se... Znas, iz Brooklyn-a si...
"Pankera".

543
00:33:11,070 --> 00:33:12,503
Secas se ?

544
00:33:12,670 --> 00:33:16,549
"Panker" je dugacko parce drveta svo zeleno

545
00:33:16,710 --> 00:33:20,305
tanko, ovako dugacko, farbano u zeleno,

546
00:33:20,470 --> 00:33:24,702
namazano Bog zna cim od 7 cm pa na dalje.

547
00:33:24,870 --> 00:33:27,748
Zapalimo ga pa se pravimo da pusimo.

548
00:33:27,910 --> 00:33:30,549
Bez gutanja dima, bilo je to drvo.

549
00:33:30,710 --> 00:33:34,020
Pravili smo se vazni.
To je bio "panker".

550
00:33:35,870 --> 00:33:37,383
Secam se.

551
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:40,189
Kad se pretvorio u Marlboro,

552
00:33:41,110 --> 00:33:43,146
toga se ne secam.

553
00:33:44,390 --> 00:33:48,463
Kao i vecine mog detinjstva.

554
00:33:48,670 --> 00:33:53,619
Detinjstvo mi je bilo toliko neprijatno
da se nicega ne secam

555
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:55,345
pre 31 godine.

556
00:33:55,510 --> 00:33:59,185
Osnovna skola

557
00:34:06,270 --> 00:34:07,305
Tommy...

558
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:10,779
Pete.

559
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:16,109
Peter Maloney ?

560
00:34:17,790 --> 00:34:18,700
Tommy F...

561
00:34:19,470 --> 00:34:20,266
Allez...

562
00:34:20,430 --> 00:34:21,749
Feccinimini...

563
00:34:23,390 --> 00:34:24,709
Fellini... Fanelli !

564
00:34:26,710 --> 00:34:28,701
Peter Maloney,
Midway srednja skola.

565
00:34:29,390 --> 00:34:30,823
Prvi u razredu

566
00:34:30,990 --> 00:34:32,469
u algebri.

567
00:34:32,630 --> 00:34:34,700
Covek koji razbija krive !

568
00:34:34,870 --> 00:34:36,906
- Sta je sa tobom ?
- Dobro je.

569
00:34:37,070 --> 00:34:40,949
Fakultet na Harvardu, doktorat na Yale-u,
u visim studijama,

570
00:34:41,110 --> 00:34:42,828
filozofije i biologije.

571
00:34:44,310 --> 00:34:46,062
Je'l ovo tvoja radnja ?

572
00:34:46,950 --> 00:34:47,700
Da.

573
00:34:47,870 --> 00:34:50,384
- Jos u kvartu ?
- Da obozavam ga.

574
00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:53,221
Mogu li da sednem ? Hvala.

575
00:34:54,110 --> 00:34:55,941
Moje cvike...

576
00:34:56,830 --> 00:34:59,298
predstavljaju buducnost cvikera

577
00:34:59,470 --> 00:35:01,904
za jedan deo stanovnistva.

578
00:35:02,630 --> 00:35:04,586
Obratio sam se...

579
00:35:05,950 --> 00:35:10,341
Prvo sam otisao da patentiram cvike. Jer...

580
00:35:11,150 --> 00:35:13,539
Da ti pokazem...

581
00:35:14,510 --> 00:35:17,229
Stakla su iznad.

582
00:35:17,390 --> 00:35:20,700
Ispitujemo ljude nasumice.

583
00:35:20,870 --> 00:35:23,748
I po njihovim odgovorima nalazimo

584
00:35:23,910 --> 00:35:27,346
filozofiju koja im omogucava da
bolje zive.

585
00:35:28,550 --> 00:35:31,826
Da te ispitam ?
Da ti postavim pitanja ?

586
00:35:31,990 --> 00:35:35,266
Imam kvotu.
Ucinices mi uslugu.

587
00:35:35,670 --> 00:35:36,580
Ovde ?

588
00:35:36,750 --> 00:35:38,820
Sto da ne ?

589
00:35:39,030 --> 00:35:41,305
Nemam sta da izgubim.

590
00:35:42,270 --> 00:35:44,659
Verujes li u Boga ?

591
00:35:45,270 --> 00:35:47,022
Da, verujem u Boga.

592
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:50,739
Stvarno ?

593
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:52,862
Zasto ? Ti ne verujes ?

594
00:35:53,670 --> 00:35:55,308
Mislim da Bog postoji.

595
00:35:56,310 --> 00:35:57,709
A to nisam ja.

596
00:35:59,590 --> 00:36:02,582
Kad bi neko mogao da ubije
osobu koju mrzis

597
00:36:02,750 --> 00:36:05,708
bez da ga uhvate, da li bi
to dopustio ?

598
00:36:08,110 --> 00:36:10,544
Ne zelim niciju smrt.

599
00:36:11,030 --> 00:36:12,622
Mozes mi slobodno reci.

600
00:36:12,790 --> 00:36:14,587
Vazi. Mozda...

601
00:36:15,830 --> 00:36:17,548
jedan tip.

602
00:36:17,710 --> 00:36:20,349
Uvek ima jedan majku mu !

603
00:36:20,510 --> 00:36:22,387
Jedan jebani seronja !

604
00:36:22,550 --> 00:36:24,461
Jedan jebani idiot, da.

605
00:36:24,630 --> 00:36:26,700
Gledas li svoje govno ?

606
00:36:26,870 --> 00:36:28,223
Svasta !

607
00:36:28,390 --> 00:36:30,824
Ucini mi. Gledas li ?

608
00:36:30,990 --> 00:36:32,309
Da li pravis...

609
00:36:32,790 --> 00:36:35,350
"Ladje od 30 cm!"

610
00:36:35,510 --> 00:36:39,025
Ne zelis da je ostavis,
das joj ime.

611
00:36:39,870 --> 00:36:42,703
Gledam. Kao i svi drugi.
I ti, zar ne ?

612
00:36:42,870 --> 00:36:45,338
I te kako !

613
00:36:46,430 --> 00:36:48,944
Bio sam na lansiranju rakete

614
00:36:49,110 --> 00:36:51,021
Kad je poletala...

615
00:36:51,390 --> 00:36:53,620
stavio sam dVogled

616
00:36:54,030 --> 00:36:56,783
u ram mojih cvika :
nema stakala.

617
00:36:56,950 --> 00:36:58,906
Svi naucnici su me pitali :

618
00:36:59,070 --> 00:37:02,460
"Gde mogu da nadjem takve cvike ?"

619
00:37:02,630 --> 00:37:06,145
Svi su imali one odvratne kanapcice
oko vrata

620
00:37:06,310 --> 00:37:09,461
sa cvikama sto vise ili uzdignute
na njihovoj celi.

621
00:37:10,350 --> 00:37:12,102
Kad sam u restoranu...

622
00:37:12,910 --> 00:37:15,185
podnignem stakla da bih citao jelovnik.

623
00:37:15,350 --> 00:37:17,989
Pitaju me :
"Odakle vam te cvike ?"

624
00:37:18,150 --> 00:37:20,584
Shvatio sam gde mi je buducnost.

625
00:37:21,790 --> 00:37:26,466
U proizvodnji ramova za cvike.

626
00:37:26,630 --> 00:37:30,339
Ili da me sponzorise fabrika ramova.

627
00:37:30,670 --> 00:37:33,707
Hteo sam da nazovem firmu :
"Luovo oko".

628
00:37:34,190 --> 00:37:36,545
Jesi li zadovoljan svojim penisom ?

629
00:37:37,270 --> 00:37:41,058
To je vrlo licno pitanje !

630
00:37:41,230 --> 00:37:43,824
Niko nece znati da si to ti.

631
00:37:43,990 --> 00:37:46,379
- Ko ce da vidi ovo ?
- Kompjuter.

632
00:37:46,910 --> 00:37:47,467
Ne.

633
00:37:47,630 --> 00:37:50,349
Nisi zadovoljan ?

634
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:53,264
Obim ? Duzina ?

635
00:37:53,430 --> 00:37:54,704
Medju nama ?

636
00:37:56,030 --> 00:37:58,828
Duzina je OK.
Debljina onako.

637
00:37:58,990 --> 00:38:01,868
I malo je nakrivljen na levo.

638
00:38:02,430 --> 00:38:03,545
Imas krivog ?

639
00:38:03,710 --> 00:38:05,701
Znas, malo je nagnut.

640
00:38:07,550 --> 00:38:08,903
"Potkovica" !

641
00:38:09,070 --> 00:38:12,426
Koliko bi trazio da pojedes ciniju govana ?

642
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:17,670
To nikad ne bih uradio.

643
00:38:17,830 --> 00:38:22,950
Svi imaju svoju cenu, ali ne ja.
Ne Tommy Fanelli.

644
00:38:23,150 --> 00:38:26,267
- Ne volis govna.
- To je protiv moje vere.

645
00:38:27,910 --> 00:38:29,548
Koje vere ?

646
00:38:30,350 --> 00:38:32,784
Zdrav razum, Peter.

647
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:36,188
Trebao bi da probas.

648
00:38:37,030 --> 00:38:40,306
Izbacili su me.
Slusaj dobro.

649
00:38:40,630 --> 00:38:44,259
U ludom drustvu zdrav covek
se cini lud.

650
00:38:47,190 --> 00:38:50,580
Ludilo je logika jakog duha...

651
00:38:57,110 --> 00:38:58,509
Premoren.

652
00:38:59,350 --> 00:39:01,341
- Oliver Wendell Holmes!
- Valjda.

653
00:39:01,510 --> 00:39:04,024
Boze moj, Tommy ! Hvala.

654
00:39:04,190 --> 00:39:07,148
Jedna od stvari koje vidjas u Brooklyn-u

655
00:39:07,310 --> 00:39:10,620
i to nisam vidjao nigde drugde u zemlji

656
00:39:10,790 --> 00:39:13,350
a to su plasticne kese po drvecu.

657
00:39:13,510 --> 00:39:17,469
To me izludjuje.
Za mene je to zastava...

658
00:39:18,110 --> 00:39:21,182
haosa. Kesa na drvetu, to je simbol.

659
00:39:23,030 --> 00:39:26,147
Pre kad bih to video, nervirao bih se.

660
00:39:26,430 --> 00:39:30,582
Jednog dana sam se setio da se mogu
skinuti sa drveca.

661
00:39:30,750 --> 00:39:34,504
Sa jednim ortakom smo napravili "kesohvatac".

662
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:40,142
Uostalom patentirali smo ga, jer se
niko pre nije setio.

663
00:39:40,310 --> 00:39:41,459
Odlicno funkionise.

664
00:39:41,630 --> 00:39:43,666
To je dugacka aluminijumska sipka...

665
00:39:43,830 --> 00:39:46,902
sa dometom od vise od 15 metara.

666
00:39:47,070 --> 00:39:49,186
Zabavno. A jos se i bavis sportom.

667
00:39:49,350 --> 00:39:53,138
Teglis se, puno hodas.

668
00:39:53,310 --> 00:39:56,859
I to ulepsava okolinu.
Poboljsava drvece.

669
00:39:58,150 --> 00:40:00,459
Evo tipicne "kese na drvetu".

670
00:40:00,630 --> 00:40:03,986
Snimite ovo. Kesa je tu.

671
00:40:04,150 --> 00:40:05,663
Kad se vratite,

672
00:40:05,830 --> 00:40:09,266
to ce biti samo slika na filmu

673
00:40:09,430 --> 00:40:11,546
jer cu ja da skinem kesu odatle.

674
00:40:12,110 --> 00:40:13,384
Je'l vam to zivotni cilj ?

675
00:40:13,550 --> 00:40:17,509
Vise kao hobi. Nesto sto radim s ortacima.

676
00:40:17,670 --> 00:40:18,705
Bas zabavno.

677
00:40:18,870 --> 00:40:20,462
I vrlo zadovoljavajuce.

678
00:40:20,630 --> 00:40:25,385
Pre, kad bih ugledao tako nesto,
rekao bih : "Opet kesa !"

679
00:40:25,550 --> 00:40:29,099
A sad kazem sebi :
"Neces ti jos dugo !"

680
00:40:29,510 --> 00:40:32,900
Dolari i zdrav razum

681
00:40:33,550 --> 00:40:38,021
Davno, bila je base-ball ekipa u Brooklyn-u.

682
00:40:43,070 --> 00:40:44,298
Jackie Robinson,

683
00:40:44,470 --> 00:40:47,303
slavni broj 42, prvi crnac

684
00:40:47,470 --> 00:40:51,383
u velikoj ligi, jos uvek odusevljava
njegovom smeloscu.

685
00:40:52,710 --> 00:40:55,702
Kad su Dodgersi napustili Brooklyn...

686
00:40:56,030 --> 00:40:58,988
mislim da goreg dana od tog nije bilo.

687
00:40:59,190 --> 00:41:01,226
Mozda kad je rat izbio.

688
00:41:01,390 --> 00:41:05,269
Inace nije bilo goreg dana za Brooklyn

689
00:41:05,430 --> 00:41:08,979
od onog kad su se Dodgersi
preselili u Kaliforniju.

690
00:41:09,270 --> 00:41:10,988
I kad su srusili Ebbets Field.

691
00:41:11,390 --> 00:41:16,225
Bio je jedinstven. Stadijum je licio
na stare sportske krugove.

692
00:41:16,510 --> 00:41:17,909
Svi su se poznavali.

693
00:41:18,070 --> 00:41:22,063
"Dodgers Symphony" su bili radni ljudi
koji su isto tako svirali

694
00:41:22,230 --> 00:41:24,744
trube, bubnjeve,

695
00:41:24,910 --> 00:41:28,425
bez pretenzija. Obozavali smo ih.

696
00:41:28,590 --> 00:41:32,947
Svi igraci su ziveli ovde.
Nisu svi bili iz Brooklyn-a.

697
00:41:33,110 --> 00:41:37,069
Ziveli su u Bedford Avenue,
najmili su stanove

698
00:41:37,230 --> 00:41:39,664
blizu stadijuma, oko Ebbets Field-a.

699
00:41:39,830 --> 00:41:41,058
Svi su ih znali.

700
00:41:41,230 --> 00:41:45,667
"Ej, Duke Snider... Jackie...
Kako je ?" Prava familija.

701
00:41:46,390 --> 00:41:48,506
Sad?
Nema vise base-ball-a u Brooklyn-u.

702
00:42:11,910 --> 00:42:15,425
To je puno para.
Bio bih lud da odbijem.

703
00:42:16,110 --> 00:42:19,944
Posle 19 godina otici ovako ?
Ne mogu da verujem !

704
00:42:20,710 --> 00:42:22,746
To su dolari i centi !

705
00:42:23,350 --> 00:42:26,626
Ova radnja radi na stetu.
Isto dobro znas kao i ja.

706
00:42:27,430 --> 00:42:29,227
Ali imas puno love.

707
00:42:29,990 --> 00:42:32,299
Svi tvoji posedi na Long Island-u ?

708
00:42:32,990 --> 00:42:35,504
Radnju mozes da skines sa poreza !

709
00:42:35,670 --> 00:42:38,184
Prekasno.
Vec smo skoro potpisali ugovor.

710
00:42:42,230 --> 00:42:46,189
Znaci "Brooklyn Cigar Company"
ce da postane radnja bioloske hrane ?

711
00:42:48,430 --> 00:42:50,022
Vremena se menjaju.

712
00:42:50,870 --> 00:42:53,748
Zbogom tabak, zdravo psenico.

713
00:42:54,550 --> 00:42:57,860
Mozda to i ne bude tako lose za tebe...

714
00:42:59,150 --> 00:43:01,141
Mozda je vreme da odes.

715
00:43:03,590 --> 00:43:07,265
Ne zelim da te gledam kako staris tu.

716
00:43:08,070 --> 00:43:10,026
Svi starimo.

717
00:43:10,190 --> 00:43:12,704
Zar je vazno gde ?

718
00:43:20,070 --> 00:43:22,106
Nema vise besplatnih cigara, ha ?

719
00:43:23,630 --> 00:43:28,340
Trebao bi stvarno da razmislis
pre nego sto odlucis, Vincente.

720
00:43:30,110 --> 00:43:34,183
Naravno, to je samo jedna mala radnjica
iz kvarta...

721
00:43:34,350 --> 00:43:36,147
Ali svi dolaze ovde.

722
00:43:36,710 --> 00:43:38,109
Ne samo pusaci.

723
00:43:38,270 --> 00:43:40,943
Deca kupuju bombone.

724
00:43:41,110 --> 00:43:43,943
Stara gospodja McKenna po svoje novine.

725
00:43:44,110 --> 00:43:46,499
Ludi Lui po svoje bombone protiv kaslja.

726
00:43:46,990 --> 00:43:49,299
Frank Diaz, po svoj "El Diario".

727
00:43:49,470 --> 00:43:52,382
Debeli Mr Chen po ukrstenice.

728
00:43:52,630 --> 00:43:56,589
Ceo kvart dolazi ovde.
Ovo nam je mesto gde se druzimo.

729
00:43:57,070 --> 00:43:59,186
To ucvrscava odnose.

730
00:44:00,310 --> 00:44:02,983
20 ulica odavde, deca se kokaju

731
00:44:03,150 --> 00:44:04,868
da bi ukrali jedan drugom patike.

732
00:44:05,430 --> 00:44:08,945
Ako zatvoris, to je ekser vise u kovcegu.

733
00:44:10,510 --> 00:44:12,944
Doprineces ubijanju kvarta.

734
00:44:15,590 --> 00:44:18,229
Pokusavas da me okrivis ?

735
00:44:19,390 --> 00:44:21,301
Ne, iznosim ti cinjenice.

736
00:44:22,230 --> 00:44:23,902
A ti sa njime radi sta hoces.

737
00:44:30,870 --> 00:44:33,338
Ovaj Ogi ce me doterati do ludila.

738
00:44:34,870 --> 00:44:39,500
Ja sve lepo dogovorim, a on
mi svira violinice !

739
00:44:40,270 --> 00:44:41,339
Brooklyn !

740
00:44:43,510 --> 00:44:46,547
Ja treba da brinem za Brooklyn !

741
00:44:47,990 --> 00:44:51,266
Cak vise i ne zivim u tom usranom gradu !

742
00:44:58,310 --> 00:44:59,538
Kako si, Vinnie ?

743
00:45:00,790 --> 00:45:01,779
Jackie ?

744
00:45:03,230 --> 00:45:04,788
Glavom i bradom, ortak.

745
00:45:06,550 --> 00:45:09,508
Jackie, najslavniji igrac base-ball-a.

746
00:45:10,990 --> 00:45:14,027
Molio sam se za tebe svaki dan
kad sam bio klinac.

747
00:45:14,510 --> 00:45:17,343
Ja sam covek koji je promenio Ameriku.

748
00:45:18,070 --> 00:45:20,709
A to sam uradio ovde u Brooklyn-u.

749
00:45:21,670 --> 00:45:24,389
Pljuvali su me, psovali,

750
00:45:24,870 --> 00:45:26,940
prosao sam kroz pakao.

751
00:45:27,270 --> 00:45:29,147
Nisam imao pravo da se bunim.

752
00:45:31,630 --> 00:45:33,109
Izjeda te...

753
00:45:33,470 --> 00:45:34,823
da budes zrtva.

754
00:45:36,070 --> 00:45:39,187
Umro sam sa 53, Vinnie.

755
00:45:39,870 --> 00:45:41,940
Mladji nego ti sad.

756
00:45:43,110 --> 00:45:45,670
Ali sam bio strasan igrac, ha ?

757
00:45:46,110 --> 00:45:48,943
Najbolji, Jackie.
Bio si najbolji !

758
00:45:49,830 --> 00:45:51,627
Stvari su se promenile posle mene.

759
00:45:52,230 --> 00:45:55,188
Ne samo za crnce, za belce isto.

760
00:45:55,510 --> 00:45:56,579
Posle mene...

761
00:45:56,990 --> 00:45:59,265
belci i crnci

762
00:45:59,430 --> 00:46:02,308
se vise nisu isto odnosili.

763
00:46:03,790 --> 00:46:06,862
I to se dogodilo ovde, u Brooklyn-u.

764
00:46:08,790 --> 00:46:11,827
I onda su odselili ekipu.

765
00:46:13,190 --> 00:46:16,660
To mi je skoro slomilo srce.
Zasto tolika glupost ?

766
00:46:16,830 --> 00:46:19,105
Za dolare i cente.

767
00:46:20,830 --> 00:46:22,786
Ebbets Field vise ne postoji,

768
00:46:23,310 --> 00:46:24,902
ali ono sto se tamo dogodilo

769
00:46:25,070 --> 00:46:26,981
i dalje zivi u nama.

770
00:46:27,390 --> 00:46:31,622
To je vazno.
Pobeda duha nad materijalnim.

771
00:46:32,070 --> 00:46:35,301
Ima i vaznijeg od base-ball-a
u zivotu.

772
00:46:36,030 --> 00:46:36,746
Ali...

773
00:46:37,790 --> 00:46:39,303
Brooklyn mi se cini u formi.

774
00:46:39,990 --> 00:46:42,424
Kao i poslednji put kad sam bio tamo.

775
00:46:43,670 --> 00:46:45,786
I Prospect Park, tamo...

776
00:46:46,750 --> 00:46:48,866
je jos uvek onako lepo.

777
00:46:51,630 --> 00:46:53,143
Kazi mi, Vinnie...

778
00:46:53,830 --> 00:46:56,867
Je'l jos prave "Belgian Waffles" ?

779
00:46:57,190 --> 00:47:02,105
Sta bih dao da zagrizem jednu !

780
00:47:02,550 --> 00:47:06,065
Sa sladoledom od pistaca i
koluticima banane !

781
00:47:07,270 --> 00:47:09,340
Kako mi to fali !

782
00:47:09,950 --> 00:47:13,340
"Belgian Waffles" ?
Jos ih prave.

783
00:47:13,830 --> 00:47:16,981
Na dve ulice odavde, u "Cosmic Diner"-u.

784
00:47:17,310 --> 00:47:20,780
Napravice ti kakve god pozelis.

785
00:47:20,950 --> 00:47:22,065
Hvala, druze.

786
00:47:24,110 --> 00:47:25,782
I meni se dopada zamisao.

787
00:47:26,910 --> 00:47:31,745
Jedan dan u Brooklyn-u bi bio promasen
bez jedne "Belgian Waffle" !

788
00:47:36,910 --> 00:47:41,938
Svaki dan 7 999 "Belgian Waffle"

789
00:47:42,110 --> 00:47:44,783
su pojedene po restoranima
u Brooklyn-u.

790
00:47:44,950 --> 00:47:49,023
Kultura Wafflesa u Belgiji je
dosta komplikovana.

791
00:47:49,190 --> 00:47:51,863
Cesto ispecemo citavu turu

792
00:47:52,030 --> 00:47:53,179
i jedemo ih hladne.

793
00:47:53,350 --> 00:47:56,023
Ne jedemo ih za dorucak,

794
00:47:56,190 --> 00:47:57,828
nego kao biskvite.

795
00:47:57,990 --> 00:48:01,903
Jedemo ih uz kafu popodne.

796
00:48:02,070 --> 00:48:04,140
Belgijski Waffle koji je poznat ovde,

797
00:48:04,310 --> 00:48:06,585
sa puno jagoda i slaga,

798
00:48:06,750 --> 00:48:10,743
zaprepasti uvek Belgijance.

799
00:48:10,910 --> 00:48:13,788
Belgijanci vole belgijski waffle,

800
00:48:13,950 --> 00:48:17,943
ali za njih su one americke bez pogovora.

801
00:48:18,110 --> 00:48:22,069
Imaju malo od "holivudske superprodukcije",

802
00:48:22,230 --> 00:48:26,109
A takvo preterivanje ne lici na belgijance.

803
00:48:37,990 --> 00:48:41,585
Cigarete nas podsecaju da smo smrtni.

804
00:48:41,750 --> 00:48:46,619
Svaki dim je jedan momenat koji prolazi,
jedna minula misao.

805
00:48:47,070 --> 00:48:51,860
Kad pusis, dim nestaje.
A to te podseca

806
00:48:52,390 --> 00:48:55,188
da je ziveti u isto vreme i umirati.

807
00:48:55,350 --> 00:48:56,829
Nedostajace mi to.

808
00:48:56,990 --> 00:48:59,345
Ali ovo je poslednja.
Sa tobom Ogi.

809
00:49:03,270 --> 00:49:04,100
Sranje...

810
00:49:05,750 --> 00:49:07,945
Ne radi vise. Imas vatre ?

811
00:49:23,870 --> 00:49:26,179
L.S. jednako M.F.T.

812
00:49:26,910 --> 00:49:29,549
Lako Sranje, Meni Fali Toalet.

813
00:49:31,310 --> 00:49:32,629
Na primer.

814
00:49:32,790 --> 00:49:36,180
Kad smo bili klinci, to bismo 
govorili o Lucky Strike-u.

815
00:49:36,790 --> 00:49:37,905
Pise ovde.

816
00:49:38,990 --> 00:49:40,139
Rekao sam ti.

817
00:49:41,470 --> 00:49:44,303
Ovo mi se svidja isto : "Dobro sprzeno".

818
00:49:46,550 --> 00:49:49,906
Bas nas zajebavaju !

819
00:49:50,310 --> 00:49:51,459
Je'l ukusna ?

820
00:49:51,630 --> 00:49:52,824
Super.

821
00:50:03,470 --> 00:50:04,698
Idemo.

822
00:50:05,390 --> 00:50:07,665
Trideset sekundi iznad Tokija.

823
00:50:09,430 --> 00:50:10,829
Bacajte bombe !

824
00:50:13,110 --> 00:50:15,578
- Pljugu ?
- Hvala, ostavio sam.

825
00:50:17,430 --> 00:50:19,819
Ebbets Field,
"sveto mesto Flatbush-a",

826
00:50:19,990 --> 00:50:22,743
bice zamenjen zgrada.

827
00:50:27,390 --> 00:50:28,539
Taj stari stadijum,

828
00:50:28,710 --> 00:50:31,224
koji je dominirao 50 godina,
ce da nestane.

829
00:50:32,230 --> 00:50:34,266
Tu gde su brujali navijaci,

830
00:50:34,430 --> 00:50:37,024
neka druga ekipa ce ici u pohode.

831
00:50:42,870 --> 00:50:47,341
Iskopali su mermer koji ce biti
za muzej base-ball-a.

832
00:50:47,510 --> 00:50:51,219
Na proslavi, Roy Campanella,
kao i bivsi Dodgersi,

833
00:50:51,390 --> 00:50:53,904
Tommy Holmes, Ralph Branca
i Carl Erskine,

834
00:50:54,710 --> 00:50:58,305
prisustvuju mirno destrukciji
njihovog igralista.

835
00:51:00,830 --> 00:51:02,502
Lopta je opet u igri.

836
00:51:02,670 --> 00:51:05,707
Ali ne ona za kojom navijaci lude.

837
00:51:11,790 --> 00:51:14,543
Ovog puta Ebbets Field je gotov.

838
00:51:59,670 --> 00:52:02,582
Rodjendan mi je.
Imam 18 godina.

839
00:52:07,950 --> 00:52:10,100
Lepo od vas.
Prvi ste.

840
00:52:10,550 --> 00:52:12,939
Brooklyn ce da se brine o meni veceras.

841
00:52:13,110 --> 00:52:16,989
Ako kazem da mi je rodjendan, ljudi
ce to da slave.

842
00:52:17,150 --> 00:52:20,347
Vatrometi ce da budu hici.

843
00:52:20,950 --> 00:52:25,660
Bombardovacemo se jajima i carapama
punim brasna.

844
00:52:25,830 --> 00:52:27,661
Tako cemo slaviti.

845
00:52:27,830 --> 00:52:32,062
Moj kolac necu pojesti :
dobicu ga u facu,

846
00:52:32,230 --> 00:52:36,701
sa udarcima carapama,
kad budem ulazila u zgradu,

847
00:52:36,870 --> 00:52:38,667
i jaje uz to.

848
00:52:40,310 --> 00:52:41,504
Provedite lep dan !

849
00:52:41,670 --> 00:52:43,900
- Srecan rodjendan !
- Hvala.

850
00:52:44,070 --> 00:52:49,781
Slusajte me

851
00:52:54,590 --> 00:52:57,150
Kako me palis...

852
00:52:59,110 --> 00:53:02,261
Iznutra se sva tresem.

853
00:53:06,950 --> 00:53:09,464
Bio bi tako divan,

854
00:53:10,750 --> 00:53:13,059
da si drugaciji.

855
00:53:14,910 --> 00:53:16,184
Taj Ogi...

856
00:53:17,190 --> 00:53:20,865
Taj Ogi, izludjuje me !

857
00:53:25,070 --> 00:53:27,345
Prvo da, pa onda ne.

858
00:53:27,510 --> 00:53:29,466
Radi, pa ne radi.

859
00:53:29,870 --> 00:53:31,701
"Mozda neki drugi put."

860
00:53:32,310 --> 00:53:36,189
Ali Ramon, nije drugi put.

861
00:53:36,990 --> 00:53:39,948
Ide da igra kod Freddy-ja sesnaestog.

862
00:53:40,110 --> 00:53:43,944
I sad Agosto kaze da je prezauzet
sesnaestog.

863
00:53:51,590 --> 00:53:53,421
Sta se dogadja ?

864
00:53:53,870 --> 00:53:56,100
Je'l on gluv ?

865
00:53:57,310 --> 00:54:00,780
Zamaram se bez veze...

866
00:54:00,950 --> 00:54:03,669
i to nicemu ne sluzi.

867
00:54:08,070 --> 00:54:09,344
Zakljucaj vrata.

868
00:54:10,110 --> 00:54:11,782
Hocu da ih zakljucas.

869
00:54:12,510 --> 00:54:14,341
Sta ti je ?

870
00:54:15,910 --> 00:54:18,982
Necu da pricam s tobom.
Nemam sta da ti kazem.

871
00:54:20,350 --> 00:54:22,102
Ne pustaj ga unutra.

872
00:54:22,270 --> 00:54:22,861
Vinnie ?

873
00:54:23,030 --> 00:54:25,590
Gde je lova ?
Znam da je ima.

874
00:54:26,190 --> 00:54:29,660
Znam da ima tajni stek.

875
00:54:30,550 --> 00:54:31,699
I ovo uzimam.

876
00:54:31,870 --> 00:54:34,748
Stani, to mi je danasnji pazar !

877
00:54:35,030 --> 00:54:36,986
- Sta radis ?
- Uzimam pare.

878
00:54:37,150 --> 00:54:38,378
Rekla sam ti.

879
00:54:39,070 --> 00:54:41,630
Idem u Las Vegas sama.

880
00:54:42,030 --> 00:54:45,625
On nece da ide.
Znaci idem ja za Las Vegas,

881
00:54:45,790 --> 00:54:50,022
i mogla bih tamo i da ostanem.
Razumes ?

882
00:54:50,550 --> 00:54:51,744
Sta se dogodilo ?

883
00:54:52,270 --> 00:54:55,342
Rekla sam ti. On je seronja !

884
00:54:55,510 --> 00:54:58,820
Idem da se zabavljam.
Idem u Las Vegas,

885
00:54:58,990 --> 00:55:01,743
cekacu da vidim Wayna Newton-a...

886
00:55:01,910 --> 00:55:05,539
I skocicu na tog rasnog pastuva !

887
00:55:05,710 --> 00:55:07,940
Dosta mi je, zelim da se zabavljam.

888
00:55:08,110 --> 00:55:12,149
Ne govori nista. Prosli put nisi 
imao sta da mi kazes.

889
00:55:12,310 --> 00:55:15,939
Nemam sta da ti kazem. I nemam sta
njemu da kazem, ti ces.

890
00:55:16,110 --> 00:55:21,138
Tvoj zivot nikad nije dosadan ?
Sve sto radis te uzbudjuje ?

891
00:55:22,110 --> 00:55:24,863
Sve te ispunjava ?
Sve je ekstra ?

892
00:55:25,030 --> 00:55:27,225
Sve je "Super, Albert" ?

893
00:55:27,390 --> 00:55:28,903
Lepo mi je ovde.

894
00:55:30,550 --> 00:55:33,701
Ne verujem.
Znam te odavno.

895
00:55:33,870 --> 00:55:35,542
Ne verujem da ti je lepo ovde.

896
00:55:35,990 --> 00:55:39,869
Kao prijateljica ti kazem.
bilo bi ti bolje negde drugde.

897
00:55:40,670 --> 00:55:41,864
A gde to na primer ?

898
00:55:42,190 --> 00:55:44,658
Mogao bi da nadjes i bolje.

899
00:55:44,830 --> 00:55:49,745
Bilo bi ti bolje u Las Vegas-u.
Tamo je bolje.

900
00:55:50,750 --> 00:55:52,786
Da li bi posao sa mnom ?

901
00:55:53,630 --> 00:55:54,426
Sta ?

902
00:55:54,590 --> 00:55:56,467
Imam para.

903
00:55:57,150 --> 00:55:59,948
Stvarno zasluzujes da budes voljen !

904
00:56:00,110 --> 00:56:04,900
Stvarno. Znam da sad nisi.
Ja bih mogla.

905
00:56:09,110 --> 00:56:13,183
Mogla bih... Daj mi dim.
Mogla bih da te lepo volim.

906
00:56:14,310 --> 00:56:16,426
Hoces li sa mnom u Las Vegas ?

907
00:56:19,270 --> 00:56:20,544
Boze mili, Dot.

908
00:56:22,830 --> 00:56:24,627
Hoces li sa mnom u Las Vegas ?

909
00:56:28,470 --> 00:56:30,222
Hoces li sa mnom u Las Vegas, duso ?

910
00:56:30,390 --> 00:56:32,585
A sta radim svom prijatelju ?

911
00:56:32,750 --> 00:56:35,787
Svi imaju prijatelje.
Imas dovoljno prijatelja.

912
00:56:38,030 --> 00:56:40,100
To nije u redu. Dot, ne !

913
00:56:40,270 --> 00:56:42,147
Ne, Dot, to nije u redu.

914
00:56:42,470 --> 00:56:46,224
Puno te volim, stvarno.
Ali to nije u redu.

915
00:56:46,470 --> 00:56:47,903
Nije u redu.

916
00:56:48,510 --> 00:56:50,341
Slusaj, nista i nije u redu.

917
00:56:50,670 --> 00:56:53,423
Nista na ovom jebanom svetu
nije u redu.

918
00:56:53,590 --> 00:56:55,979
Stvari koje su lose su OK.

919
00:56:56,150 --> 00:56:59,938
Moglo bi da bude lepo.
Oduvek sam zelela da te poljubim.

920
00:57:00,150 --> 00:57:01,663
Oduvek sam zelela.

921
00:57:01,830 --> 00:57:04,549
Ne mogu da kazem da nisam.

922
00:57:08,310 --> 00:57:10,187
Hocu da prekines !

923
00:57:10,350 --> 00:57:12,181
Jebi se ! Idem !

924
00:57:23,070 --> 00:57:25,061
Sranje...

925
00:57:28,630 --> 00:57:29,585
Sta je ?

926
00:57:30,310 --> 00:57:31,299
Sta ?

927
00:57:31,510 --> 00:57:32,704
Sta se dogadja ?

928
00:57:33,630 --> 00:57:36,098
Jesi li video Dot kad je izasla ?
Bila je ovde.

929
00:57:36,270 --> 00:57:37,862
Nista mi nije rekla.

930
00:57:38,030 --> 00:57:40,498
Izgledala je otkaceno.

931
00:58:02,430 --> 00:58:06,025
Razumes sta pricam ?
Jesi li gluv ?

932
00:58:10,790 --> 00:58:12,781
- Ne ides.
- Zasto ?

933
00:58:12,950 --> 00:58:15,100
Sta ti je ?

934
00:58:15,990 --> 00:58:18,140
- Idem u Las Vegas.
- Sta ces da radis tamo ?

935
00:58:18,310 --> 00:58:21,461
Da se bavim show business-om.
Da se provodim !

936
00:58:21,630 --> 00:58:24,019
Druge stvari sem gledanja tebe

937
00:58:24,190 --> 00:58:25,748
kako buljis u jebani TV !

938
00:58:25,910 --> 00:58:27,423
Hoces da se bavis show-business-om ?

939
00:58:27,590 --> 00:58:29,626
Tako nesto !

940
00:58:29,790 --> 00:58:33,465
Ne govorim sa njim.
Kazi mu da ne govorim sa njim.

941
