01:13:53,390 --> 01:13:55,187
Na Brooklyn-ski nacin sad !

1179
01:14:00,830 --> 01:14:03,298
Glumci

1180
01:15:22,790 --> 01:15:24,508
Jos pusis ?

1181
01:15:24,670 --> 01:15:26,183
Ne udisem dim.

1182
01:15:41,070 --> 01:15:42,788
Odbij majmune !

1183
01:15:44,350 --> 01:15:47,262
